Annotation Interface FormatBottom

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({TYPE_USE,TYPE_PARAMETER}) @TargetLocations({LOWER_BOUND,UPPER_BOUND}) @SubtypeOf({Format.class,InvalidFormat.class}) @DefaultFor(LOWER_BOUND) public @interface FormatBottom
The bottom type in the Format String type system. Programmers should rarely write this type.
See the Checker Framework Manual:
Format String Checker, the bottom type
